belgolux trade move into surplu in 1986 the belgo-luxembourg econom union ( bleu ) move into a narrow trade surplu of 4.7 billion franc in 1986 after a 140.4 billion franc deficit in 1985 , figur given by a spokesman for the nation statist institut show . he said import fell last year to 3,061.8 billion franc from 3,304.1 in 1985 while export were also lower at 3,066.6 billion franc against 3,163.7 billion . in decemb , the bleu had an 11.9 billion franc trade surplu after a 10.9 billion franc surplu in novemb and a 2.3 billion franc surplu in decemb 1985 .